T*
(do AI agents programmatically register with services? That?s the question Auth.md aims to) Tj
T*
(answer. It?s a single Markdown file you host at your domain that tells agents how to register) Tj
T*
(your users, which flows you support, what scopes you expose, and how credentials get issued.) Tj
T*
(It?s like robots.txt but for agent registration. Cloudflare, Firecrawl, and Resend have already) Tj
